{"tid":1503332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門第五任行政長官選舉 唯一候選人民心所向高票當選","createTime":"2019-08-25T02:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T02:59:52.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65dcadf4932e8054f73afa1f332fefd16c9ef495","tid":1503332,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:56:37.000Z","msg":"澳門第5任行政長官選舉今日(25日)早上10時在澳門東亞運體育館舉行，賀一誠是選舉唯一候選人。400名選舉委員會委員全體出席，並於早上約10時25分完成投票，隨即開始點票。 <br />\n<br />\n賀一誠已取得過半數選票支持，肯定當選。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190825/mobile/bkn-20190825082838493-0825_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190825%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190825082838493-0825_00822_001.html&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUB5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=e97f8364\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190825/mobile/bkn-20190825082838493-0825_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1a8baf75ad69c74db8ef2f55fe9fd4487f10b84f","tid":1503332,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"民主選舉真係好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7f2afa86ddaf9f0aac3602f997b79c24cd6295","tid":1503332,"uid":160166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdaedf09cdebb4d3b4c5cc1202c7b9d76464abbd","tid":1503332,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:59:52.000Z","msg":"投票人400位，候選人1位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}